Title of the project :- BASIC CALCULATOR
objective:- To create a basic calculator that performs addition,substraction,multiplication,division operations.
Describe data:- The data consist of two numbers and an operator provided by the user.
CODE:-

# Python programm for Basic Calculator 
first_num=float(input("please enter first number:"))
operator= input("please enter operator")
second_num=float(input("please enter second number:"))

if operator =="+":
    print(first_num + second_num)
elif operator == "-":
    print(first_num - second_num)
elif operator == "*":
    print(first_num * second_num)
elif operator == "/":
    print(first_num / second_num)
elif operator == "%":
    print(first_num % second_num)
else:
    print("Invalid Oerator")
